     <div type="quotations">
   <pb facs="2"/>
   <q>
      <bibl>Luc. <hi>14.</hi>
      </bibl>
      <p>Euery one of you which doth not renoūce all thinges which he hath, cannot be my Disciple.</p>
   </q>
   <q>
      <bibl>Mat. <hi>16.</hi>
      </bibl>
      <p>If any man will come after me, let him deny him-selfe, and take vp his Crosse, and follow me.</p>
   </q>
   <q>
      <bibl>Luc. <hi>14.</hi>
      </bibl>
      <p>Many man come vnto me and doth not hate his father and mother, and wife, and children, and brethren and sisters, <gap reason="illegible" resp="#keyers" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>ea and moreouer his owne life, he can<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>not be my Disciple.</p>
   </q>
</div>
